Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.77,0:00:05.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:13.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.69,0:00:33.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.44,0:00:36.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The sound resonates\NInto my heart, so hard and deep
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.31,0:00:40.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A field of stars spans endlessly\NAnd through it I carve a passageway
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.31,0:00:42.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In step with time as generations change
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.31,0:00:44.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Close your eyes and listen closely
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.31,0:00:47.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shooting stars stream on silently…\Nuntil the goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.31,0:00:50.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Keep the light inside of you,\Nnever give up don't ever lose
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.31,0:00:52.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Transcend time and you will prove,\Nthere is a special place for you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.27,0:00:54.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A blaze of glory is there,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.07,0:00:55.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's all a part of our estate;\Nlife is our story to create
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.86,0:01:01.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.77,0:01:05.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wishes speak from ages old by voice of light\NThroughout the age, never fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.69,0:01:09.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A secret fire, a scream of light,\Nvoices calling through twilight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.40,0:01:11.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Cast your thoughts to the wind,\Nhang your wishes on the moon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.52,0:01:13.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Live your life with all your strength\Nfor dreams will reach you very soon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.48,0:01:16.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.07,0:01:19.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wishes speak from ages old\Nby voice of light
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.27,0:01:21.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Throughout the age,\Nnever fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.31,0:01:24.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Someday your dream will find\Nits place somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.82,0:01:28.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Keep shining like a star
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.00,0:01:37.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.16,0:01:38.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.87,0:01:43.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll shoot you guys into\Nthe Seireitei with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.51,0:01:45.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,From the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.69,0:01:47.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sky?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.69,0:01:47.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sky?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:50.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Kukaku Shiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.01,0:01:53.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the best pyrotechnic in\NRukon District!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.36,0:02:03.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Pyrotechnic?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.42,0:02:05.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.65,0:02:08.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Koganehiko! Shiroganehiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.17,0:02:11.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.16,0:02:17.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.79,0:02:21.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Yes! Yes! Yes! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.62,0:02:22.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.40,0:02:23.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.83,0:02:25.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.44,0:02:27.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The floor…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.48,0:02:29.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,is rising!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.76,0:02:35.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Yes! Yes! Yes! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.76,0:02:35.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Yes! Yes! Yes! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.60,0:02:38.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Yes! Yes! Yes! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.60,0:02:38.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Yes! Yes! Yes! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.82,0:02:40.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The ceiling is…opening!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.67,0:02:42.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is this for real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.08,0:02:46.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Yes! Yes! Yes! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.08,0:02:46.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Yes! Yes! Yes! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.31,0:02:52.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Yes! Yes! Yes! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.31,0:02:52.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Yes! Yes! Yes! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.48,0:02:55.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Yes! Yes! Yes...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.48,0:02:55.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Yes! Yes! Yes...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.47,0:03:02.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you kids scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.29,0:03:05.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is the special Kukaku Shiba\NSuper-sized Fireworks Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.80,0:03:08.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Flower-Crane Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.05,0:03:10.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say it before I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:13.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.16,0:03:16.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What, speechless?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.57,0:03:20.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of joke is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.62,0:03:22.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You may be a fireworks expert\Nor whatever,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.04,0:03:26.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but as if you could shoot us\Nover with that--!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.97,0:03:32.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:34.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Reishu-kaku, Spirit Core.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.01,0:03:38.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Place your palms on it and\Nfocus your spiritual energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.69,0:03:40.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.62,0:03:47.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How do you focus\Nyour spiritual energy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.50,0:03:49.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.80,0:03:51.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.27,0:03:53.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you're a Soul Reaper,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.32,0:03:55.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,surely you know how to\Nuse your Kido.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.03,0:03:55.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Actually…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.98,0:03:56.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.71,0:04:00.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This boy is the newbie Soul Reaper\NI told you about earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.65,0:04:03.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He can't use Kido at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.77,0:04:05.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:06.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.24,0:04:12.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Geez! How hopeless!\NGanju, show him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.58,0:04:13.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.74,0:04:14.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, give it here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.41,0:04:19.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why you--!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.16,0:04:23.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kid! Wanna fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.17,0:04:26.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah… Take it if you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.32,0:04:29.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather die than be\Nshown by you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.04,0:04:32.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.92,0:04:34.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.92,0:04:34.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.96,0:04:44.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.76,0:04:48.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.08,0:04:53.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Cannonball.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.11,0:04:55.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Cannonball?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.28,0:04:57.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.81,0:05:03.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You think that the only thing guarding\Nthe Seireitei is that barrier,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.46,0:05:05.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but you're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.79,0:05:08.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That barrier is made from\Nan ore known as Sekki–Seki
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.22,0:05:10.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,that is rare even in Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.67,0:05:13.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is a fragment of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:16.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.91,0:05:18.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,it completely breaks down\Nspiritual energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.30,0:05:20.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's why it's impossible
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.97,0:05:23.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,to bore a hole through\Nthe barrier with spiritual energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.83,0:05:24.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.16,0:05:28.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,even when cut,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.69,0:05:31.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,it emits a wave that breaks down\Nspiritual energy from all sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.84,0:05:35.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...that the Seireitai has\Na spherical barrier around it
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:40.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,from the sky to\Nthe underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.83,0:05:45.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And so…that’s where this comes in!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.24,0:05:49.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sis…I'm tired--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.92,0:05:51.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Deal with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:56.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Special Hard Spiritual Partition\NPenetration Device that I invented.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.57,0:05:57.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:06:01.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,if all of you combined put your spiritual\Nenergy into this Spirit Core,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.07,0:06:04.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,you can create a temporary cannonball\Nthat will break through the barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.83,0:06:05.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And then…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:09.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll shoot that cannonball\Nwith the Flower-Crane Cannon
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.25,0:06:12.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and it'll pierce straight\Nthrough the barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.51,0:06:18.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Any questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.30,0:06:20.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Err…well…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.34,0:06:22.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right, you are dismissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.02,0:06:23.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Go to the underground training room
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.43,0:06:25.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and practice concentrating\Nyour spiritual energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.71,0:06:27.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.71,0:06:27.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.62,0:06:28.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Take them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:29.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:29.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.79,0:06:32.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.78,0:06:33.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.86,0:06:35.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch me! Leggo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.86,0:06:35.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Put me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.46,0:06:38.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, if any one of you\Nloses concentration,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.56,0:06:40.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,you'll blow up right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.54,0:06:41.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.88,0:06:42.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You all need practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.69,0:06:44.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Practice hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.86,0:06:47.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you never mentioned that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.55,0:06:50.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.16,0:06:51.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sis…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.16,0:06:54.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Go down below and\Nhelp them practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.86,0:06:58.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sis…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.06,0:07:02.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really gonna help them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.00,0:07:04.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.43,0:07:08.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm against it!\NHelping a Soul Reaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.87,0:07:11.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What'll I say to Brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:13.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.15,0:07:13.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ganju!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.67,0:07:18.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I told you…\NDon't ever speak of it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.54,0:07:20.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sis…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.52,0:07:22.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you understand, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.04,0:07:25.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Listen…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.46,0:07:30.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Never show such\Na weak face in front of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.63,0:07:42.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.92,0:07:44.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I've had to wear the\NLieutenant badge.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.37,0:07:46.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.08,0:07:50.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s the first time I've been\Nordered to wear it like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.33,0:07:53.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,"Lieutenants are to\Nput on their badges
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.87,0:07:56.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and wait in the aid’s room #2."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:07:58.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is getting interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.16,0:08:05.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Abarai… Iba…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.11,0:08:08.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hinamori. No one else\Nshowed up yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.90,0:08:10.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.13,0:08:18.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenants are scattered all over\NSoul Society working diligently.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.29,0:08:22.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It might take about half a day\Nfor everyone to gather.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.04,0:08:26.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My Captain can't be reached at all.\NWhat a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.42,0:08:32.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Who is your\Nsquad captain again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.79,0:08:34.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You know, the Hitsugaya boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.55,0:08:39.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that little prodigy. That’s tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:40.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Abarai…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.91,0:08:41.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.71,0:08:44.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen our Captain Aizen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.25,0:08:47.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.58,0:08:51.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's been acting strange lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.67,0:08:53.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.78,0:08:56.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But he won't answer when\NI ask him if anything's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.03,0:08:59.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.95,0:09:03.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.57,0:09:04.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.81,0:09:06.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing's the matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.66,0:09:10.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even this summons will probably\Nbe cancelled soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.29,0:09:10.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.41,0:09:15.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In your view, should she die?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.00,0:09:20.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? Just what the hell\Nis going on, Captain Aizen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.68,0:09:24.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Training Room\N		No! That's wrong, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.82,0:09:26.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's not "wohhh."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.82,0:09:29.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's nuahh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.80,0:09:28.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nuohh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.33,0:09:32.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, no!  Nuahh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.57,0:09:34.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nuohh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.02,0:09:35.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.20,0:09:37.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.50,0:09:39.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's nuahhh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.36,0:09:40.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nuahhh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.58,0:09:42.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nuahhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.16,0:09:46.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t understand!\NExplain it better!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.58,0:09:53.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.40,0:09:57.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided to help\Nthat Soul Reaper,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.30,0:10:01.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,like the one who killed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.25,0:10:03.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you were alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.99,0:10:09.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and saw me not helping them,\Nyou'd scold me, wouldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.29,0:10:14.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You…who loved Soul Reapers\Nand died as a Soul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.06,0:10:29.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now, please Orihime.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.14,0:10:35.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! You're doing just fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.51,0:10:36.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.14,0:10:40.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite narrow,\Nbut the shape is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.71,0:10:46.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm…The shape probably\Nreflects his personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.15,0:10:47.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Next! Chad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.54,0:10:54.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this is…a bit unstable,\Nbut very powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.99,0:10:57.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And finally, Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.84,0:11:04.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.30,0:11:05.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:06.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.76,0:11:07.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,...supposed to be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.51,0:11:09.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can only conclude that\Nyou have no talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.92,0:11:11.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No talent at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.92,0:11:11.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No talent at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.15,0:11:15.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shirogane!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.08,0:11:17.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I said I don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.85,0:11:20.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You! Teach me some useful pointers,\Ndamn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.04,0:11:40.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, Brother…dinner's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.59,0:11:46.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Hey guys!\NDinner is ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.50,0:11:48.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You must be hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.42,0:11:49.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.96,0:11:52.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't get to eat in\NRukon District, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.93,0:11:57.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys can't use spiritual energy.\NSo they don't get hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.06,0:11:58.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Go and eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.43,0:12:00.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.78,0:12:01.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.26,0:12:07.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Go and eat.\NI'll come, after I figure this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.92,0:12:10.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Okay then…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.36,0:12:11.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.62,0:12:13.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue, you're coming, too right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.04,0:12:18.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm not hungry at all yet,\Nso it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.06,0:12:24.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Heh…I'm lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.59,0:12:27.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I am a bit hungry…\NOh, how embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.83,0:12:28.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.71,0:12:32.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Go. I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.93,0:12:36.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,N-No… I want to practice some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.91,0:12:39.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really not hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.33,0:12:40.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.33,0:12:43.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.05,0:12:48.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.16,0:12:54.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Okay…\NSince you're asking me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.58,0:12:57.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.70,0:12:59.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey Inoue!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.14,0:13:01.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, Ishida. Chad, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.16,0:13:27.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.34,0:13:28.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is she that important to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.88,0:13:29.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.10,0:13:34.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This Soul Reaper you're going to save.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.36,0:13:36.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.87,0:13:37.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.86,0:13:38.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Give it here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.17,0:13:43.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then did you, like,\Npromise to save her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.75,0:13:44.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.11,0:13:46.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then it must be money.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.83,0:13:49.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She promised to pay you\Nif you saved her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:52.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No way I can use money\Nfrom here in my world!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.89,0:13:56.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then why?\NWhy are you so determined?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.12,0:13:57.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I owe her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.07,0:14:06.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She saved my life.\NAnd I haven't repaid her yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.96,0:14:10.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She gave me her power to\Nsave my family and me…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.02,0:14:12.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,even though she had just met me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.56,0:14:15.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Because of that, she was arrested…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.33,0:14:18.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and she's about to be executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.37,0:14:25.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to turn into a pathetic guy\Nwho'd turn his back on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.54,0:14:29.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.12,0:14:32.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.89,0:14:33.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.57,0:14:35.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?!\NGive it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.29,0:14:37.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to practice, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.24,0:14:39.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Cover your ears!\NDon't you dare listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.49,0:14:44.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to review the trick\NI developed myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.08,0:14:45.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.08,0:14:49.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Visualize this…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.62,0:14:52.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Draw a circle in your heart…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.40,0:14:56.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,as dark as possible,\Nand as heavy as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.73,0:15:03.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then…imagine yourself jumping right\Ninto the center of the circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.17,0:15:13.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is the basic image\Nthat works for all Kido.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.70,0:15:27.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.86,0:15:30.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's so easy I could cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.09,0:15:32.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't even have to practice it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.58,0:15:36.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.33,0:15:43.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What a ham!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.16,0:15:46.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Such terrible acting! Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.50,0:15:56.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Draw a circle…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.61,0:15:59.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,in my heart…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.78,0:16:08.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.50,0:16:09.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.50,0:16:13.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Inoue, are you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.58,0:16:16.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, I'm full--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.94,0:16:25.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,See? My stomach is full.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.38,0:16:29.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You don't have to go that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.28,0:16:31.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Forget I ever asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.16,0:16:37.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Actually…I was going to\Ntake it to Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.83,0:16:40.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Kurosaki still hasn't…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.91,0:16:47.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! It's breaking apart!\NNo! The object!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.76,0:16:50.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Great Kukaku arm pillar\Nis going to fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.51,0:16:53.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s Kurosaki…!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.21,0:16:56.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.37,0:17:03.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?! Hey Ganju!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.24,0:17:06.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry, Sis…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.82,0:17:12.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I just showed him once.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.80,0:17:15.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I never imagined it would\Nturn out like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.54,0:17:29.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You fool! Gather your spiritual energy\Ntogether already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.67,0:17:41.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.56,0:17:45.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You did it, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.49,0:17:46.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.48,0:17:51.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!\NDon't lose your concentration!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.16,0:17:52.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.59,0:18:00.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you listening to me, fool?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.94,0:18:02.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.20,0:18:04.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you lose concentration,\Nyou’ll blow up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.17,0:18:06.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.90,0:18:09.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll say, you…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.50,0:18:11.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're just as guilty, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.92,0:18:13.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you, no food tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.74,0:18:15.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.40,0:18:16.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why put me together with him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.96,0:18:18.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Got a problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.95,0:18:22.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Owee! Okay, we understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.25,0:18:22.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.07,0:18:31.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.38,0:18:38.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain of the Squad 3…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.62,0:18:41.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Gin Ichimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.71,0:18:43.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.87,0:18:47.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I get called so suddenly…\Nand look at this crowd?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.01,0:18:54.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The captains who control Soul Society…\Nare all here for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.23,0:18:57.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.16,0:19:02.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Captain of the\NSquad 13 isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.88,0:19:04.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.45,0:19:07.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's absent with an illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.42,0:19:10.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Again? I hope he gets better soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.78,0:19:12.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Quit joking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.44,0:19:14.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You know you weren't summoned\Nhere for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.73,0:19:19.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I understand you went and\Nplayed with the Ryokas by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.35,0:19:23.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And I hear you failed. Explain yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.89,0:19:27.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You should have no trouble dealing\Nwith four or five Ryokas.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.16,0:19:31.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, they didn't die then?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.74,0:19:32.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.73,0:19:36.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I thought they were dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.46,0:19:38.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My intuition has gotten dull.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.33,0:19:42.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You can stop that monkey business.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.37,0:19:46.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no way that\Ncaptain-level guys like us
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.15,0:19:50.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,would fail to tell instantly whether\Nan opponent's Hakudo has ceased or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.61,0:19:54.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There they go again,\Nstupid squabbling among old fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.71,0:19:59.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! You make it sound like\NI let him go on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.25,0:20:02.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's precisely what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.44,0:20:03.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, Kurotsuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.87,0:20:07.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking to him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.63,0:20:10.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Or do you want to be done in by me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.85,0:20:12.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.32,0:20:13.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.16,0:20:17.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh boy…\Ntempers are running high.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.68,0:20:22.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Enough of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.55,0:20:29.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I think the reason why\Nyou have been summoned
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.60,0:20:31.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,has been made clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.29,0:20:38.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Acting alone,\Nand letting the target escape…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.83,0:20:42.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well? How do you defend\Nyour actions…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.96,0:20:44.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichimaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.33,0:20:47.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.00,0:20:49.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.50,0:20:51.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing I can say\Nto defend myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.85,0:20:56.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I made a simple mistake.\NI won't make excuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.29,0:20:57.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll accept whatever punishment--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.76,0:20:59.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just a minute, Ichimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.11,0:21:03.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,First, let me ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.85,0:21:11.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Urgent alert! Urgent alert!\NIntruders in Seireitei!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.32,0:21:14.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All Squads get into position!\NRepeat…!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.63,0:21:18.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Intruders?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.62,0:21:20.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Those Ryokas?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.29,0:21:21.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.54,0:21:32.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.57,0:21:46.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With much appreciation
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.44,0:21:48.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,send a rhapsody filled\Nwith treasured thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.77,0:21:52.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To the people who have\Nalways held me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.19,0:21:54.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.31,0:21:56.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.31,0:21:58.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever I may be
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.31,0:22:00.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll always be grateful for who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.48,0:22:03.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was casually walking through town
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.73,0:22:05.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Around the time dusk fell\Nand the city was bathed in red
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.82,0:22:07.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It was an afternoon with\Ncrowds of people coming and going
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.02,0:22:09.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know why but\NI just stood there and watched
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.82,0:22:12.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then my cell phone started to vibrate\Nand I made myself move
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.31,0:22:14.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,hoping it could fill\Nin this hole in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.31,0:22:16.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’re not alone\NYou see, everybody
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.52,0:22:18.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta hold each other up
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.57,0:22:20.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With much appreciation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.90,0:22:23.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I send a rhapsody filled\Nwith treasured thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.23,0:22:26.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To the people who have\Nalways held me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.31,0:22:28.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.36,0:22:30.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.57,0:22:32.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever I may be
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.48,0:22:34.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll always be grateful for who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.37,0:22:39.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Four students and one cat\Ninto Seireitei!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.49,0:22:41.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Got it! I'm off, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.27,0:22:43.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Attention, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.07,0:22:45.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Cannonball will be shot very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.31,0:22:48.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Guests, take your seats now or else!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.24,0:22:50.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really worried.